Here's a way to express your gratitude:

---

Hi [Manager's Name],

Thank you so much for acknowledging my efforts. Your support and guidance have been invaluable, and I genuinely appreciate the encouragement and direction you've provided. It makes a huge difference to know my work is valued, and I feel fortunate to have you as a manager. Looking forward to contributing even more under your leadership!

Best regards,  
[Your Name]

---

This message conveys your gratitude in a warm and professional way. Let me know if you'd like any adjustments!
